"central and peripheral nervous system, part a. this class includes one or more of 4 standard radiation therapy interventions or procedures related to the central and peripheral nervous system.  these interventions or procedures are listed in the world health organizations international statistical classification of diseases and related health problems or icd-10 pcs under code d0.. . "
"central and peripheral nervous system, part a. this class includes one or more of 4 standard radiation therapy interventions or procedures related to the central and peripheral nervous system.  these interventions or procedures are listed in the world health organizations international statistical classification of diseases and related health problems or icd-10 pcs under code d0.. beam radiation of spinal cord using electrons. this classification denotes the group of activities that yields a radiation therapy intervention or procedure of beam radiation of spinal cord using electrons.this intervention or procedure is listed in the world health organizations international statistical classification of diseases and related health problems or icd-10 as code d0063zz. "

"

"
